      "title": "Woman jumps into Embilipitiya Lake with two sons",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A 32-year-old woman had jumped into the Chanrika Wewa in Embilipitiya with her two children.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said one her sons, a five-year-old boy died, and the other 11-year-old boy is being treated at the Embilipitiya Hospital.",
        "The mother is currently being treated at the Embilipitiya Hospital\u2019s Intensive Care Unit.",
        "The woman and her eleven year old son were rescued by the Sri Lanka Police Life Saving Division."
